cciOption.help:
Enables compression for specified type. Default: rdc_rst_dest_rst_clk
		-enable src
			:Groups the violations for each unique source {SrcObject}
		-enable dest
			:Groups the violations for each unique destination {DestObject}
		-enable src_dest_rst
			:Groups the violations for an unique pair of source reset and destination reset {AllSrcResets, RdcDestResets}.
		-enable container
			:Groups the violations for each unique module {ContainerInstance, Module}
		-enable src_rst_dest_clk
			:Groups the violations between an unique pair of source reset and destination clock {AllSrcResets, DestClockInfoList}
		-enable rdc_rst_dest_rst_clk
			:Groups the violations between an unique pair of RDC source reset {RdcSourceResets}, destination reset {RdcDestResets} and destination clock {DestClockInfoList}
